---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import programming from "../../assets/Programming.png";
---

<section class="py-16 md:py-24  text-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-7xl">
    
   

    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-10 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-20">
      
      <div class="flex-1 text-center lg:text-left space-y-6 md:space-y-8">
        
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-transparent bg-clip-text text-white">
            Programar: el mas obvio
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <p class="text-lg text-left md:text-xl lg:text-2xl text-purple-100 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 mx-auto">
          Me gusta programar porque me permite crear soluciones y transformar ideas en proyectos reales. Siempre hay algo nuevo que aprender.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex-1 flex justify-center items-center w-full max-w-md lg:max-w-none">
        <div class="relative group w-full">
          
          <div class="relative bg-purple-800/30 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-2xl p-4 md:p-6 border border-white/20 shadow-2xl">
            <Image 
              src={programming} 
              alt="Programación - Código en pantalla" 
              class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-lg object-cover aspect-video"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style is:global>
  .group:hover .blur-xl {
    transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
  }
</style>